list.item:
This means: 

—substantial concessions to the Buddhist formula for a
                                constitutional gathering;

—maintenance of the unity of the Directorate;

—probably—but not necessarily—the replacement of Ky, who has shown guts and some
                                political sensitivity;

—then, at the right moment, a countrywide curfew, backed, if
                                necessary, by U.S. forces, to permit the constitutional group to
                                work.
